item.description: MAC Blog Files fitmath.github.io is a static website built using Hugo by Jonathan Goldfarb. Go here to get hugo. This repository hosts the files used to generate the blog portion of fitmath.github.io; cloning [the main repository]() is the best way to go about editing these files. Getting Started To get started, clone this repository using git, e.g. from the folder into which you would like FITMath.github.io to appear, run
